\section{Pattern of spring stiffnesses for the {LP}\ ball and spring model}

Here we give a precise description of the pattern of coupling strengths in a {LP}\ ball-and-spring model, corresponding to the structure in Fig.~\ref{fig:5-periodic_removed}(c). 

